    "Case 5 (ODS mimic) received the lowest TDSs for both ChatGPT 3.5 (3[1.75]) and Chat-GPT4 (2.5 [1.25]), though ChatGPT 4 showed a similarly low TDS for ODS case 2 (2.5 [3.25]).",
    "Note that for case 2, it was the only time ChatGPT 4 received a TDS of 0 from multiple evaluators.",
